snippet.title: Survival Nation - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Survival Nation is an open-world online RPG survival game designed for VR. 
In this game, you will kill hundreds of zombies, acquire weapons, learn new skills, craft, explore the world, complete quests, and most importantly, fight for survival. 
Will you join a Survival Nation?

Steam page:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2153780/Survival_Nation/

Join our Discord server to be updated.
https://discord.gg/w3g3Pjk4DF
